content:
# I successfully harvested 10 units of Coal, and my inventory now contains:
# - Coal: 10
# - Stone: 5
# - Iron Ore: 20

# Now that I have enough coal, I can return to the Stone Furnace and insert the coal to fuel it. 
# I will move back to the furnace's position at (0, 0) and then insert the coal.

move_to(Position(x=0, y=0))  # Moving back to the Stone Furnace's position.
insert_item(Prototype.Coal, Position(x=0, y=0), quantity=5)  # Inserting 5 coal into the furnace to fuel it.
